task.summary: Improved progressbar when updating balance. Close #12
New cover photo in Navigation Drawer
Take only first word when return new barcode
Added graphs and estimations to counter
Fixed estimations on 32 bits, added method to download from url in ConnectionHelper
Refactor padding of dialogs and use system resources for the cancel string
Added expiration date and last update of card. Close #10 close #15
Update all values when updating card balance
Fixed not scrolling smoothly in balance
Added renovation section and refactoring help
Removed Swipe to Refresh from Balance
Added ZXing dependency for barcodes, added show barcode and removed Vision. Close #17
Improved show barcode. Caching Bitmaps in internal storage
Added little docs and reorder code. Close #18
Do not update name on updateUserBalance
New online help, removed the old
Improved UX, now don't display expiration date in 1970 and -1 of balance
Don't display expiration date in 1970 or -1 of balance
